OL,6,FCases of norovirus in Cardiff last
OL,7,Fyear were caused by swimming in
OL,8,FCardiff Bay, the city council has
OL,9,Fconfirmed.
OL,11,FCardiff Council scrutiny committee
OL,12,Fmembers raised concerns last week
OL,13,Fabout the poor water quality at
OL,14,FCardiff Bay, which ultimately led to
OL,15,Fan inflatable obstacle course which
OL,16,Fwas based there having to move.
