OL,6,FOne councillor speaking at the
OL,7,Fcouncil's environmental scrutiny
OL,8,Fcommittee meeting on Thursday,
OL,9,FSeptember 11, said the issue was
OL,10,Fharming the ability for the Bay to be
OL,11,Fused by members of the public and
OL,12,Fbusinesses.
OL,14,FThe fresh water lake, impounded by the
OL,15,FCardiff Bay Barrage in 2000, is fed by
OL,16,Fthe River Ely and River Taff which
OL,17,Fhave both suffered from sewage
OL,18,Fdischarges in recent years.
