OL,6,FOn the day of the meeting, Cllr
OL,7,FLancaster said he noticed four out of
OL,8,Fthe six stations where monitoring
OL,9,Ftakes place recorded a 'fail' for
OL,10,Fwater quality.
OL,12,F"It's not really good enough, is it?"
OL,13,Fsaid the councillor.
OL,15,F"There's a real danger that poor
OL,16,Fquality is harming the ability of the
OL,17,FBay to be used by the citizens of
OL,18,FCardiff and businesses.
