OL,6,F"Surely there should be some sort of
OL,7,Fattempt to address that and not just
OL,8,Fsay, 'well it's coming from up
OL,9,Fstream... it's out of our hands'."
OL,11,FData published on the CHA's website
OL,12,Ffor Monday, September 15, showed all
OL,13,Fsix monitoring stations recorded a
OL,14,F'fail' for water quality.
