OL,6,FCardiff Council's cabinet member for
OL,7,Fculture, sports and parks, Cllr
OL,8,FJennifer Burke, read out a statement
OL,9,Fon Cardiff Bay at last week's
OL,10,Fenvironmental scrutiny committee
OL,11,Fmeeting.
OL,13,FShe said in the summer of 2024,
OL,14,Ffollowing a series of illnesses, an
OL,15,Fincident management team chaired by
OL,16,FPublic Health Wales identified
OL,17,Fnorovirus as the cause.
