OL,6,FA council report on water quality at
OL,7,FCardiff Bay states: "The current
OL,8,Fmonitoring programme looks for
OL,9,Findicators of sewage contamination,
OL,10,Ftherefore it is presumed that the
OL,11,Fsource of norovirus in the environment
OL,12,Fwould be sewage related.
OL,14,F"It would be expected that there is
OL,15,Fsome protection afforded by the
OL,16,Fcurrent monitoring regime in respect
OL,17,Fto viruses."
