OL,6,FEarlier this year, a research
OL,7,Fprogramme was initiated with Bangor
OL,8,FUniversity to look at testing for
OL,9,Fnorovirus in Cardiff Bay.
OL,11,FIn response to Cllr Lancaster's
OL,12,Fcomments, Cllr Burke said: "I don't
OL,13,Fthink it's fair to say that we're just
OL,14,Fthrowing our hands up and saying
OL,15,F'we're not doing anything'.
OL,17,F"Cardiff Council are working in
OL,18,Fpartnership and pushing back on Welsh
OL,19,FWater and Natural Resources Wales.
