OL,6,FThe water-based inflatable assault
OL,7,Fcourse first opened on Cardiff Bay in
OL,8,F2022 and welcomed hundreds of visitors
OL,9,Feach summer.
OL,11,FIt moved to Cosmeston Lakes near
OL,12,FPenarth on a trial basis this year.
OL,14,FIn March, a spokesperson for the CHA
OL,15,Fsaid: "Recent summers have been very
OL,16,Fwet and this increased rainfall, and
OL,17,Fthe higher river flows that results
OL,18,Fin, have increased the number of
OL,19,Ffailed tests.
